{"name":"Two-Face","nameCn":"双面人","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/d9/60/30113_crt_ZrAmv.jpg","info":"<li><span>简体中文名: </span>双面人</li><li><span>别名: </span>哈维·丹特</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Harvey Dent</li><li><span>性别: </span>男</li>","detail":"双面人是一位出现在DC漫画中的超级反派，蝙蝠侠的敌人。人物首次登场于《侦探漫画》#66，由鲍勃·凯恩与比尔·芬格创作。<br />哈维·丹特原为哥谭市的地方检察官，因为被黑帮老大萨尔·马洛尼泼硫酸而导致半边脸面毁容，性格失常而成为了一个罪犯。左半边脸孔有严重面部伤害，经常身穿左右两边花色不相同的西装，无论要做什么事之前都会先掷硬币决定。双面人的铜板和一般铜板不同，它只有两个人头，而其中一面有许多刮痕（代表善或恶）。双面人是一个以“噱头手法”为主的罪犯角色，常以计谋来造成混乱。","jobs":[{"href":"/subject/25461","name":"The Dark Knight","nameCn":"蝙蝠侠：黑暗骑士","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/e9/48/25461_T9xtT.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/14523","name":"Batman: The Long Halloween","nameCn":"蝙蝠侠：漫长的万圣节","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/44/f4/14523_us.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/14340","name":"Batman: Dark Victory","nameCn":"","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/d9/9f/14340_us.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/223334","name":"Batman vs. Two-Face","nameCn":"","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/4d/66/223334_3T4gG.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/108306","name":"Gotham (Season 1)","nameCn":"哥谭市 第一季","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/55/b0/108306_c4ntT.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/12083","name":"Batman: The Animated Series","nameCn":"蝙蝠侠 (1992)","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/7c/11/12083_NzaQr.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/27495","name":"Batman: Arkham City","nameCn":"蝙蝠侠：阿克汉姆之城","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/8b/86/27495_ooOdd.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/127957","name":"The New Batman Adventures","nameCn":"蝙蝠侠新冒险","cover":"//lain.bg